然后点击Apply<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-fUo-ICF7oaA/Ug3kDdu8TpI/AAAAAAAAECQ/MvfUEVFEdKY/s1600-h/4%25255B2%25255D.png"><img alt="4" border="0" height="534" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-zKeEKu9XO2w/Ug3kEDi79pI/AAAAAAAAECY/iXzsa3ZwNlc/4_thumb.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="4" width="608" /></a><br />
